  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个金融系统的核心流程图。起点是AuthVault，也就是认证保险库，所有资金操作都得先经过它。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，AuthVault作为入口节点。那认证之后资金往哪走？是直接到账本服务还是有中间环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "认证通过后，AuthVault会向LedgerService发起\"Get money\"操作获取资金。但这里有个关键点——资金到账之后要进入一个TransactionQueue做分流处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把AuthVault到LedgerService的获取资金连线加上，然后LedgerService连到TransactionQueue这个判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "TransactionQueue这里要分出三条路径，分别标记为One、Two、Three。第一条路径One走FraudDetection做风控检测。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加One分支到FraudDetection。那Two和Three分别指向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Two要回到LedgerService做最终记账，Three也要走FraudDetection，但是是另一条独立的检测通道，对应不同的风控策略。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Two到LedgerService，Three也到FraudDetection。这样FraudDetection会出现两次，一个是One分支，一个是Three分支，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，虽然都是FraudDetection，但One和Three触发的是不同的检测规则引擎，所以分成两条线更清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，Three分支已添加。我检查下整体结构：AuthVault→LedgerService（Get money）→TransactionQueue，然后分出One→FraudDetection、Two→LedgerService、Three→FraudDetection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了——AuthVault到LedgerService的箭头标签应该是\"Get money\"，但你图上好像没显示这个标签？另外TransactionQueue是菱形判断节点，不是普通方框。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "已修正：加上了\"Get money\"标签，把TransactionQueue改成菱形判断节点。现在结构应该对了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个流程图准确反映了我们的资金流转和风控分流逻辑。AuthVault统一入口，TransactionQueue做智能路由，FraudDetection双通道并行检测。",
